<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">国风·周南·麟之趾</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson9d10d0af0c97">
麟之趾，振振公子，于嗟麟兮。<br />麟之定，振振公姓，于嗟麟兮。<br />麟之角，振振公族，于嗟麟兮。
</div>
</div>
